tc_game_mods.comments:
Our robots will automatically fetch the newest version from oxidemod.org when they release each update!

Oxide 2 is a complete rewrite of the popular, original Oxide mod for the game Rust. Oxide 2 has a focus on modularity and extensibility. The core is highly abstracted and loosely coupled, and could be used to mod any game that uses .NET.

The extension also exposes a library allowing developers to access the allies feature from within other plugins. See the template plugin to quickly get started using the API.
